{"tid":1479863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華：港事務是家事 不難想像美國在港上下其手","createTime":"2019-08-17T05:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T12:00:17.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"5377ba3453cfbcd49fe3d3fcd737f9014903db2b","tid":1479863,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:22:32.000Z","msg":"反修例局面愈演愈烈，美國總統特朗普近期更將香港形勢與中美貿易戰掛勾。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華早上在電台節目表示，香港尊重和平示威比世界其他地方都大，現時香港事務是「家事」，質疑美國以經濟手法迫使香港作改變。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華又強調，香港是獨立關稅區，在貿易事務上自主處理，美方若將香港事務與貿易混為一談，不難想像美國在香港事務上下其手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2223445/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2223445%2F&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=98a1683a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2223445/</a>"},{"pid":"b3cde3568aaca3844a03f7aee08bb1550b4d7e32","tid":1479863,"uid":290297,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"5377ba3453cfbcd49fe3d3fcd737f9014903db2b","tid":1479863,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:22:32.000Z","msg":"反修例局面愈演愈烈，美國總統特朗普近期更將香港形勢與中美貿易戰掛勾。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華早上在電台節目表示，香港尊重和平示威比世界其他地方都大，現時香港事務是「家事」，質疑美國以經濟手法迫使香港作改變。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華又強調，香港是獨立關稅區，在貿易事務上自主處理，美方若將香港事務與貿易混為一談，不難想像美國在香港事務上下其手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2223445/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2223445%2F&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=98a1683a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2223445/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"翻譯佢send比Nancy"},{"pid":"f508c7b10170d994604e41de85f528d2304b2678","tid":1479863,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fced02c97